{"tid":920600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓7-11怒貼「中國人出入禁止」 告示","createTime":"2018-11-29T02:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T04:40:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"91ca24b4216c6ae2bc29932be105cf4f3c6ababa","tid":920600,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"南韓濟州島的7-11便利店門外，張貼寫有「中國人出入禁止」字句的告示，引起當地華人抗議，並向7-11總部投訴及要求拿走告示，否則將會採取「維權行動」。<br />\n<br />\n濟州華僑中國和平統一促進會會長崔勇勛說：「這明顯是對中國人的挑釁，雖然這間便利店比較隱蔽，但仍在鬧市區，臨近濟州市步行街，也會有一些中國人看到。」他已向南韓7-11總部抗議，又向該分店店長投訴，但店長卻不接電話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181129/58968975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58968975&d=U0Pt4ZSIax%2BM6%2FJa6Mfzr0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3a10fa7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F58968975&h=c3bb56c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181129/58968975</a>"},{"pid":"29cb57a6e8fa225ce06d86674d16e8bed97912a6","tid":920600,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181128/large/1543410672_92c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181128%2Flarge%2F1543410672_92c1.jpg&h=38b0b606&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"261713dd9011896383d3eb456c2a96b10b6b124c","tid":920600,"uid":39365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91ca24b4216c6ae2bc29932be105cf4f3c6ababa","tid":920600,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"南韓濟州島的7-11便利店門外，張貼寫有「中國人出入禁止」字句的告示，引起當地華人抗議，並向7-11總部投訴及要求拿走告示，否則將會採取「維權行動」。<br />\n<br />\n濟州華僑中國和平統一促進會會長崔勇勛說：「這明顯是對中國人的挑釁，雖然這間便利店比較隱蔽，但仍在鬧市區，臨近濟州市步行街，也會有一些中國人看到。」他已向南韓7-11總部抗